 would be pretty harsh to introduce a system for us while leaving them out in the cold.  Besides, they will be reliant on us to turn those runes/words/whatever into actual spells.  Just something to remember.  That being said, yeah, they did have it easy for the first 50 levels, there is no doubt about it.<br>
<br>
It's new content (sort of) so I am in favor of it.  Personally, I kind of like research and would have preferred if this system had been implemented at the beginning instead of the spell drop system.  Oh well, nobody asked me.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Silverlynx Silentfist (61st level monk)<br>
