<br>
With Ykesha, any 60 spells I am missing on Suzanna (eg 60 Pet Heal), I can have a shot at getting, even if it does involve a lot of camping, whereas previously I'd have had to save an ungodly amount of platinum to buy in the bazaar (assuming I'm ever lucky enough to see it for sale).<br>
<br>
And now, with this change, some of the 60 spells I am missing on my 63 cleric (eg Greater Remove Curse or Marzins Mark), which I would probably not get for months, if ever, I may also be able to camp drops for with Suzanna and research for her.<br>
<br>
This helps all int casters and wis casters alike in small family guilds who do not raid the huge mobs get a chance to get these spells.<br>
<br>
Sounds good to me. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
